modName: Tolfdir grey face fix for Immersive College of Winterhold - DELETED
summary: Fixes tolfdir's grey face for CWI.
descriptionHtml:
This simple file fixes a possible glitch where Toldfir's face becomes grey while using the Immersive College of Winterhold mod.

Usage:

Place the contents into your Data folder.

If this texture file doesn't work for you, follow this to do it yourselfÂ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rOXF89QtgYM.

Note that if you have another mod that modifies Tolfdir loaded after ICoW this might not work.
